info.processed.lightning_concentrator:
§7This block causes a lightning, which allows to craft new items.
This only works when the weather is thunder or a Environmental Suppressor is nearby.
info.processed.crafting_station: §7Use an processor core and an additional item to craft new processors!
info.processed.overload_station: §7This block allows you to charge Overload Tools!
info.processed.deactivated_charged_overl: §7Activate this processor using the lightning concentrator and add functionality!
info.processed.processor_assembler: §7This block allows to create processors more easily.
info.processed.environmental_processor: §7Simplifies the process of crafting with the Lightning Concentrator.
info.processed.processing_unit: §7A real processor! Is required by the Motherboard to get a function.
info.processed.environmental_suppressor: §7More crafting! This block allows you to use the Lightning Concentrator at any time when placed in a 15 block radius.
